  <brief_title>Pilot Study Evaluating Stress Response and Immune Function in Mechanically Ventilated Patients With Alcohol Use Disorders Treated With Propofol or Midazolam</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Clinical Trial Comparing Propofol and Midazolam in Mechanically Ventilated Critically Ill Patients With Alcohol Use Disorders: An Open Label Pilot Study</official_title>
