  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the effects of the sedatives propofol and midazolam on
      stress response and immune function in critically ill patients with alcohol use disorders who
      are undergoing mechanical ventilation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
